        "content": "import torch\n\n\n_cache = {}\n_cache_get = _cache.get\n\n\ndef run(rope_theta: float) -> torch.Tensor:\n    out = _cache_get(rope_theta)\n    if out is not None:\n        return out\n\n    indices = torch.arange(0, 128, 2, dtype=torch.float32, device=\"cuda\")\n    exponents = indices / 128.0\n    out = 1.0 / torch.pow(float(rope_theta), exponents)\n    _cache[rope_theta] = out\n    return out\n"
